1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,310
Want to make your accessibility statement page easier for your customers to find?

2
00:00:04,970 --> 00:00:12,650
In this video, I'll show you exactly how to add a page to your Shopify menu so your customers can access it effortlessly.

3
00:00:12,980 --> 00:00:18,480
If you're new to Shopify or just getting started, don't worry.

4
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:22,040
I'll walk you through each step clearly.

5
00:00:22,040 --> 00:00:25,970
By the end of this video, you'll know how to link any page to your store's navigation.

6
00:00:26,300 --> 00:00:28,950
Making browsing intuitive for everyone.

7
00:00:29,080 --> 00:00:33,180
Step one: From your Shopify dashboard, click on Content.

8
00:00:33,180 --> 00:00:36,400
Then select Menus.

9
00:00:36,400 --> 00:00:38,710
This is where you manage all your stores' menus.

10
00:00:38,980 --> 00:00:41,200
Step two: Choose the menu you want to edit.

11
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:46,240
For this video, we'll use the Footer Menu, which appears at the bottom of your store.

12
00:00:46,240 --> 00:00:48,770
Click on it to see the existing menu items.

13
00:00:48,970 --> 00:00:51,210
Step three: Click on Add menu item.

14
00:00:51,570 --> 00:00:55,700
Enter the name of the new item, for example, Accessibility Statement.

15
00:00:55,900 --> 00:00:59,200
Step four: Link this menu item to the page you want it to lead to.

16
00:00:59,480 --> 00:01:03,110
Since this is an accessibility statement, select your accessibility statement page.

17
00:01:03,110 --> 00:01:05,470
Step five: Click Save to update the menu.

18
00:01:05,790 --> 00:01:08,240
Step six: Go to your online store.

19
00:01:08,240 --> 00:01:10,210
And click up here to view your store.

20
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:16,630
You'll see the Accessibility Statement page successfully added to your footer menu, ready for your customers to access easily.

21
00:01:16,630 --> 00:01:22,800
Now your Shopify menu is updated and your customers can navigate your store more easily.

22
00:01:23,010 --> 00:01:25,970
Don't forget to try it yourself and make your store even more user-friendly.